# Input

```jsonc
{
	"list": [],
	"list1": [],
	"list2": [],
	"list3": [],
	"list4": [],
}

```


# Options

```json
{
  "$schema": "../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
  "json": {
    "parser": {
      "allowTrailingCommas": true
    },
    "formatter": {
      "trailingCommas": "all"
    }
  }
}
```

